The installer package for this PLATFORM is organized as follows:

    Install_Xyce_PLATFORM
    |
    |___ README
    |
    |___ install_PLATFORM.sh
    |
    |___ xtl.tar.gz



To install Xyce, from the setup directory type:

    sh install_PLATFORM.sh

and follow the instructions.



You must have standard Unix utilities (tar, gzip, sh, etc.) prior to 
installation.  Superuser privileges are not required.
